                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">Police sergeant, 52 R</hi>). The prosecutor gave the prisoner in charge for stealing razors, shaving brushes, and other articles, and he was a runaway apprentice—the prisoner said he knew nothing at all of him; he was mistaken.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I am not the person—I do not know the man at all—he fetched a lad to swear I was the person, and he could not swear to me at all.</p>
               <p>
